metadata.name: The Elaborate Dance
metadata.description:
Amber Vittoria’s abstracted work draws on her relationship to femininity, emotion, and identity. This ongoing collection comprises several physical works from Amber’s personal archive, listed as timed NFT editions ranging in pricing and edition time windows. This edition was open for 7 minutes. The poem is as follows: 

“The Elaborate Dance”  
On the inside of my eyes,  
Rivals the moves in reality,  
What a surprise. 

This artwork listed is indeed authentic, created by, and copyright to artist Amber Vittoria; the purchase of this NFT is a purchase of the asset, not of the copyright.
